doc.after: The largest site is Geocaching com owned by Groundspeak Inc which began operating on September 2 2000 With a worldwide membership and a Freemium business model the website claims millions of caches and members in over 200 countries Hides and events are reviewed by volunteer regional cache reviewers before publication Free membership allows users access to coordinates descriptions and logs for some caches For a fee users are allowed additional search tools the ability to download large amounts of cache information onto their gps at once instant email notifications about new caches and access to premium member only caches 75
